Package owltools.ncbi

Class Summary
NCBI2OWL Provides static methods for converting NCBI Taxonomy data files into OWL format.
NCBIConverter Provides common methods for working with NCBI.
NCBIOWL Provides static methods for creating and initializing an OWLOntology into which taxa can be inserted.
OWLConverter Provides common methods for converting data into Web Ontology Language (OWL) format using OWLAPI.
